# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your values.

## Backend API
```bash
# Port for backend API
PORT=3001

# API Keys (comma-separated) for authentication
VALID_API_KEYS=development-key-1,development-key-2

# CRE Workflow paths
CRE_PROJECT_ROOT=/path/to/basket_enhanced
CRE_WORKFLOW_PATH=/path/to/basket_enhanced/workflow
```

## Smart Contracts
```bash
# Private key for contract deployment (NEVER commit this!)
PRIVATE_KEY=0x...

# Admin address for basket ownership
ADMIN_ADDRESS=0x...

# Chainlink Policy Engine address
POLICY_ENGINE=0x...

# RPC Endpoints
ETH_RPC_URL=https://eth-mainnet.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_KEY
POLYGON_RPC_URL=https://polygon-rpc.com
ARBITRUM_RPC_URL=https://arb1.arbitrum.io/rpc
```

## Stablecoin Contract Addresses
```bash
# Ethereum Stablecoin Addresses
STABLECOIN_ADDRESS_ETH=0x...
MINTING_CONSUMER_ADDRESS_ETH=0x...

# Polygon Stablecoin Addresses
STABLECOIN_ADDRESS_POLYGON=0x...
MINTING_CONSUMER_ADDRESS_POLYGON=0x...

# Arbitrum Stablecoin Addresses
STABLECOIN_ADDRESS_ARBITRUM=0x...
MINTING_CONSUMER_ADDRESS_ARBITRUM=0x...
```

## POR APIs
```bash
# Staging POR API
POR_API_URL_STAGING=https://your-por-api.com/verify

# Production POR API
POR_API_URL_PRODUCTION=https://prod-por-api.com/verify
```

## Workflow
```bash
# POR (Proof of Reserve) API
POR_API_URL=https://your-por-api.com/verify

# Chainlink ACE settings
ACE_ENABLED=true

# CCIP (Cross-Chain Interoperability Protocol)
CCIP_ENABLED=true
```

## Logging
```bash
# Log level: debug, info, warn, error
LOG_LEVEL=info

# Log file path (optional)
LOG_FILE=/var/log/basket-enhanced/app.log
```

## Security
```bash
# CORS allowed origins
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000,https://example.com

# Enable rate limiting
RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED=true
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=60000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100
```

## Database (if using)
```bash
# MongoDB connection (optional, for future use)
# MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/basket_enhanced
```

## Development
```bash
# Enable verbose logging
DEBUG=basket:*

# Node environment
NODE_ENV=development
```
